	   <tr><td colspan=2>OK Guys here is how a lvl 12 Enchanter can aquire the Thicken Mana and Crystalize Mana spells (Purify Mana not in game yet). Go to Lesser Faydwer the brownie camp is just north of the fairy camp follow the trail and take the first fork right. There is a hill in front of Brownie camp entrance from this hill (safe distance Brownies KOS to all classes and races) cast alliance on every brownie you see. Cast invisi on yourself and walk into camp stand in front of merchant and cast minor illusion on self then cast alliance on merchant. Buy the spells from merchant then gate out. This is how I did it at lvl 12. and the Vials of viscouse mana sell for 15pp per vial so there is a good profit in the spell selling to tailors. The crystalize mana spell I still haven't found a purpose for it but as everyone says new things always coming. I can make a good 100pp just for casting the spell and they supplying ingredients. Something to think about. Hope this helps all.<br>Azula Silentwalker<br>27th Enchantress of The Seventh Hammer<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
