<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97409942216424></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97409942216424><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=13&mid=97409942216424>RE: The Chainmail Look!</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=13&mid=97409942216424#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Nov 13th 2:10 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I don't have all the information, only bits and pieces.<br><br>For the Enchanted Elven Chainmail Tunic you need:<br>- Essense of Moonlight (found on Dread wolves in Kithicor and undead types in MM)<br>- Vials of Swirling Mist (found on Mist elementals in Najena or Steam elementals in Steamfont)<br>- Morning Dew (foraged in Greater and Lesser Faydark, I think)<br>- Large brick of Mithral ore (needs to be enchanted by a 49+ Enchanter)<br>- Temper (to be used on the ore; skill needed: Brewing)<br>- Blue Diamond(s) - approx 250pp per gem<br>- a pattern<br>- and hopefully a skill of over 175 in blacksmithing :)<br><br>Now the numbers I'm really not sure of but here is a guess:<br>3 bricks of ore<br>2 essense of moonlight<br>1 vial of swirling mist<br>1 morning dew<br>1? blue diamond<br><br>I have an NON enchanted tunic on my character now.<br>Stats are AC 12 wt 3.0<br>But it looks really nice!<br>The enchanted stats are:<br>AC 14&nbsp;&nbsp; WIS+4  INT+4  SvMagic+2<br><br>The person who made it for me is very ill in hospital, so I can't get more detailed than that.<br>But I think they got their info from some Trade Skills board<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
